"to\": 1389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1254, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9902279901055143, \"rank\": 0.009575931052975734, \"text\": \"Pakistani\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He secured the gold medal with a javelin throw of 92.97 meters, surpassing India's Neeraj Chopra, who had won gold at the previous Olympics but took home the silver this time.\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1465, \"end\": 1470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999045031, \"rank\": 9.529136937146287e-11, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1473, \"end\": 1486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Neeraj Chopra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before his gold medal win, Arshad Nadeem's reported assets were modest, estimated at around 8 million PKR (approximately 80 lakh INR).\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistani_rupee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.939533376037986e-23, \"text\": \"PKR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistani_rupee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistani_rupee\"}, {\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_rupee\", \"score\": 0.999999686562709, \"rank\": 3.1343728578080215e-07, \"text\": \"INR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_rupee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_rupee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He owned a Suzuki car and had limited financial resources, as mentioned in various media outlets.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, following his Olympic success, his wealth has grown significantly since August 8.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a reward for his gold medal, Arshad received $50,000 (approximately 42 lakh INR or 14 million PKR).\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1971, \"end\": 1974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_rupee\", \"score\": 0.999999686562709, \"rank\": 3.1343728578080215e-07, \"text\": \"INR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_rupee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_rupee\"}, {\"begin\": 1989, \"end\": 1992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistani_rupee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.939533376037986e-23, \"text\": \"PKR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistani_rupee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistani_rupee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Punjab government announced a prize of 100 million PKR, while Punjab Governor Sardar Salim Haider Khan pledged an additional 2 million PKR.\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1999, \"end\": 2005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punjab\", \"score\": 0.9999999897963789, \"rank\": 1.0203398436222909e-08, \"text\": \"Punjab\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punjab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punjab\"}, {\"begin\": 2050, \"end\": 2053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistani_rupee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.939533376037986e-23, \"text\": \"PKR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\":